NodeJs Installation and Setup:

1. sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install build-essential libssl-dev

2. curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.31.0/install.sh -o install_nvm.sh

3. bash install_nvm.sh

4. source ~/.profile

5. nvm install 6.8.0

6.nvm use 6.8.0

7. npm install -g express

8. npm link express

9. npm install mongoose

10. npm install body-parser
